ğŸ“˜  Decision Control Instructions 
ğŸ‘‰ Used to make decisions and control the flow of execution based on conditions.

ğŸ”¹ if Statement
Executes code only if the condition is true.
if (condition) {
    // true block
}



ğŸ”¹ if...else
Choose between two blocks based on condition.
if (condition) {
    // true block
} else {
    // false block
}




ğŸ”¹ else if Ladder
Checks multiple conditions in sequence.
if (cond1) {
    // block 1
} else if (cond2) {
    // block 2
} else {
    // default block
}




ğŸ”¹ Ternary Operator ? :
Shorthand for if...else.

(condition) ? value_if_true : value_if_false;





ğŸ”¹ Logical Operators
Used to combine or compare conditions:

&& (AND)
|| (OR)
! (NOT)


